Class FeatureFrame

java.lang.Object
net.beadsproject.beads.analysis.FeatureFrame

public class FeatureFrame
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<FeatureFrame>
A FeatureFrame stores a set of features for a single chunk of audio data.
